{"tid":2202700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Youtube將設新短片分享平台\"Shorts\" 與TikTok競爭","createTime":"2020-09-14T19:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T05:08:09.000Z","uid":270889,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4859bd7e010393264833e846497d3e31470ee82f","tid":2202700,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T19:36:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Reuters/status/1305588455729057792\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReuters%2Fstatus%2F1305588455729057792&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=26ad6b52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReuters%2Fstatus%2F1305588455729057792&h=5677612b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Reuters/status/1305588455729057792</a><br />\n<br />\n(Reuters) - Alphabet Inc&rsquo;s YouTube is rolling out its version of social media rival TikTok, <span class=\"red\">a new short-form video service</span> called <span class=\"red\">Shorts</span>, enabled <span class=\"red\">within its</span> <span class=\"red\">video-sharing platform</span>.<br />\n<br />\nYouTube will <span class=\"red\">first test the feature in India</span> over the next few days and then expand to more countries in the coming months, it said in a blog post on Monday. (<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3ho1q36\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3ho1q36&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=e4b25552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/3ho1q36</a>)<br />\n<br />\nYouTube&rsquo;s new product, which will <span class=\"red\">compete with Facebook Inc&rsquo;s</span> <span class=\"red\">Reels</span> and TikTok, will let users record short mobile-friendly vertical videos and then add special effects and soundtracks pulled from a music library.<br />\n<br />\nThe announcement also comes as Oracle Corp and China&rsquo;s ByteDance team up to keep TikTok operating in the United States, beating Microsoft Corp in a deal structured as a partnership rather than an outright sale.<br />\n<br />\nYouTube&rsquo;s entry into the short-form video service space coincides with TikTok&rsquo;s ban in one of its biggest market, India, following the country&rsquo;s escalating tensions with China.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-alphabet-youtube-shorts-idUSKBN2652KC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-alphabet-youtube-shorts-idUSKBN2652KC&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=e22c8da6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-alphabet-youtube-shorts-idUSKBN2652KC&h=54b6284b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-alphabet-youtube-shorts-idUSKBN2652KC</a>"},{"pid":"82603dac202982ca41cc2f5aa311f26e6b2bc875","tid":2202700,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T19:40:35.000Z","msg":"抖音&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; all"},{"pid":"392cdb7708abb6b9382e89f15b2af0e3ccd4f342","tid":2202700,"uid":270889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"82603dac202982ca41cc2f5aa311f26e6b2bc875","tid":2202700,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T19:40:35.000Z","msg":"抖音&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; all"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T19:42:58.000Z","msg":"BAN !!"},{"pid":"37e3ee6fe29c63e1fd22a92ab21e39f7e7e56d15","tid":2202700,"uid":128102,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T19:45:36.000Z","msg":"聞說TikTok屈機在個演算法"},{"pid":"c9b23ff8e2b886a1ccfc492b9ef7f55599113e7c","tid":2202700,"uid":70487,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"37e3ee6fe29c63e1fd22a92ab21e39f7e7e56d15","tid":2202700,"uid":128102,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T19:45:36.000Z","msg":"聞說TikTok屈機在個演算法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T19:46:39.000Z","msg":"Youtube演算法世界第一"},{"pid